{"tid":1167320,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(頭皮）脂溢性皮膚炎集中討論區","createTime":"2019-05-23T03:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T03:47:35.000Z","uid":222284,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"42a3784b595757f3544dfd5144c3ae0571c3e3ae","tid":1167320,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:29:25.000Z","msg":"有左接近十年，頭皮又紅又勁大塊頭皮，用一般洗頭水絕對無效，要用藥性洗頭水，Nizoral 幾年前用有效，最近已經用到無效，要混合埋有蕉油成份既洗頭水好小小，有無人曾經有相同問題？係唔係一世都根治唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad10840385d91a2ae3e80ace4e4d09239b7d5348","tid":1167320,"uid":222284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"嚴重到眉毛，耳仔後面都有，唔係一般落雪既頭皮，係一塊塊，最大塊試過成個一毫子咁大"},{"pid":"011b14396019da2f7692273b9b0009aac3bec553","tid":1167320,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"我都係，搞到脫髮添，<br />\n而家薑黃洗頭水，少d油，<br />\n已經食埋印保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n希望減緩個速度"},{"pid":"e9871e0966604aec1ad3842f41f6e258ca241968","tid":1167320,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"011b14396019da2f7692273b9b0009aac3bec553","tid":1167320,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"我都係，搞到脫髮添，<br />\n而家薑黃洗頭水，少d油，<br />\n已經食埋印保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n希望減緩個速度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"我暫時頭髮好多，幾多歲開始脫髮？"},{"pid":"822b785f8bdc0efa370763f66828966e9ed390fc","tid":1167320,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9871e0966604aec1ad3842f41f6e258ca241968","tid":1167320,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"011b14396019da2f7692273b9b0009aac3bec553","tid":1167320,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"我都係，搞到脫髮添，<br />\n而家薑黃洗頭水，少d油，<br />\n已經食埋印保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n希望減緩個速度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"我暫時頭髮好多，幾多歲開始脫髮？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"成日好多面油頭油，<br />\n頭皮好易紅腫、痛、生頭瘡，<br />\n23開始（以前一向多面油頭油），而家29，<br />\n上年先的起心肝食藥，<br />\n頭髮明顯比23之前少左，<br />\n但而家明顯改善左"},{"pid":"49302b52a25cedba66e6fd394f778d9f6411efdb","tid":1167320,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822b785f8bdc0efa370763f66828966e9ed390fc","tid":1167320,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9871e0966604aec1ad3842f41f6e258ca241968","tid":1167320,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"011b14396019da2f7692273b9b0009aac3bec553","tid":1167320,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:32:46.000Z","msg":"我都係，搞到脫髮添，<br />\n而家薑黃洗頭水，少d油，<br />\n已經食埋印保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n希望減緩個速度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"我暫時頭髮好多，幾多歲開始脫髮？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"成日好多面油頭油，<br />\n頭皮好易紅腫、痛、生頭瘡，<br />\n23開始（以前一向多面油頭油），而家29，<br />\n上年先的起心肝食藥，<br />\n頭髮明顯比23之前少左，<br />\n但而家明顯改善左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:38:21.000Z","msg":"我全部症狀都有，只係無脫髮問題，頭皮問題點搞？"},{"pid":"1fec65bb44c55b79fa3fef990641939d69453672","tid":1167320,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49302b52a25cedba66e6fd394f778d9f6411efdb","tid":1167320,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822b785f8bdc0efa370763f66828966e9ed390fc","tid":1167320,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9871e0966604aec1ad3842f41f6e258ca241968","tid":1167320,"uid":222284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"我暫時頭髮好多，幾多歲開始脫髮？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"成日好多面油頭油，<br />\n頭皮好易紅腫、痛、生頭瘡，<br />\n23開始（以前一向多面油頭油），而家29，<br />\n上年先的起心肝食藥，<br />\n頭髮明顯比23之前少左，<br />\n但而家明顯改善左"},"